data.description: Hard to beat the location of this 5BR/3BA home in Willhaven Estates.  Just 2 minutes to Fort Gordon main gate. Easy access to everywhere from here. This home is clean and well maintained.  Freshly painted and new roof. This home features a huge owner suite with space for a sitting room, office or home gym. Luxurious owner bath with garden tub, shower and double vanity.   Three more spacious bedrooms upstairs and an additional guest bedroom on the main level.  Open concept common areas feature a large living room with wood buring fireplace open to breakfast room and kitchen.  Plenty of cabinets and counterspace here.  Dining room with cofferred ceilings and heavy moulding is off the kitchen and open to the two story foyer.   Exterior spaces include large covered front porch and fenced level back yard.  Community ammenites include pool and playground.
